<br>
This is what I think we should do. Forigve all my mistakes but I am typeing that at 12:43 in the morning lol.<br>
<br>
LEVEL: Ok well first I though we should cut the minium level to 40. But we would have 4 members left. So lets go a little bit lower but try to stay as high as possible. 20.  By 20 people will know how to play the game and alot about it. This should help with everyone trying to be around the same level. <br>
<br>
EVENTS: I know we have a new event person. Trajhen I think. Hes doing a very good job so far. As he said we need to have different groups with different levels in each of them. Say A 20-30 B 31-40 C41+ . And Have each month one week will be an A week, One week will be a B week, one week will be a C week, one week will be a &quot;charity week&quot; where we goto zones and help out As much as posible, and on the last two days we have the guild meeting, like officers meeting the day before and events tournaments and meeting the next day. Also make a rule in the new ZTP about if u do not attend 1 event per month u will be suspened from guild, if it happens again removal. I dont want people in my guild that dont want to be apart of it and be involved.<br>
<br>
ZTP: Yes it has a few flaws in it. But it was put there for a reason. To keep us strong. We can add to it if we want. But try not to redo it. That is our base. That is our standards. Without that there wouldn't be an silver hawks. Changing it to Verants lets all get along policys isn't going to cut it. We need to make our own rules that are fit for our guild.<br>
<br>
<br>
THINGS NEEDED TO BE WORKED ON- #1 Recruiting #2 Events #3 Keeping people happy<br>
<br>
ADDITIONS- Maybe we should do our recruiting like other guilds have done. You need a minium of 7 member sponserships to get in. You are put in on a 30 day testing period. Where we will get to know you and see if u like it, but if u do one thing wrong in those 30 days your out after that you are a full time member and follow by the normal rules or somthing.<br>
<br>
Well some of these may work and some might not.<br>
<br>
-Oman<br>
